org.lockout.UserRequest
org.lockout.Login
class Login extends UserRequest
Login related methods here. Not much really, creates an instance of User somewhere and uses it to make basic calls. Prepares, response object that will be used for setting Router.response that is finally returned to Handler.handleRequest(org.lockout.LambdaInput, com.amazonaws.services.lambda.runtime.Context)
